quran[13{c,v,t}:
27,1,toy seen yeh ayaat hain quran aur kitaab Mubin ki
27,2,hadaayat aur basharat unn imaan laane walon ke liye
27,3,"jo namaz qaim karte aur zkoh dete hain, aur phir woh aisay log hain jo akhirat par poora yaqeen rakhtay hain"
27,4,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log akhirat ko nahi mantay un ke liye hum ne unn ke krtoton ko khushnuma bana diya hai, is liye woh bhataktay phir rahay hain"
27,5,yeh woh log hain jin ke liye burii saza hai aur akhirat mein yahi sab se ziyada khasaray mein rehne walay hain
27,6,aur ( aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) bilashuba tum yeh quran aik hakeem o Aleem hasti ki taraf se pa rahay ho
27,7,"( aِnhin uss waqt ka qissa sunaaoo ) jab moose ne apne ghar walon se kaha ke"" mujhe aik aag si nazar aayi hai, mein abhi ya to wahan se koi khabar le kar aata hon ya koi angara chunn lata hon taakay tum log garam ho sakuu """
27,8,"wahan jo pouncha to nida aayi ke"" mubarak hai woh jo is aag mein hai aur jo is ke mahol mein hai pak hai Allah , sab jahanon ka parvar-digaar"
27,9,"ae moose, yeh mein hon Allah , zabardast aur Dana"
27,10,"aur pheink to zara apni laathi"" jounhi ke moose ne dekha laathi saanp ki terhan bil kha rahi hai to peeth phair kar bhaga aur peechay murr kar bhi nah dekha"" ae moose, daro nahi mere huzoor rasool dara nahi karte"
27,11,ila yeh ke kisi ne qasoor kya ho phir agar buraiee ke baad uss ne BHALAI se apne fael ko badal liya to mein maaf karne wala meharban hon
27,12,"aur zara apna haath apne garibaan mein to daalo chamakta howa niklay ga baghair kisi takleef ke yeh ( do nishanain ) no nishanion mein se hain firaon aur is ki qoum ki taraf ( le jaane ke liye ), woh barray bad kirdaar log hain """
27,13,magar jab hamari khuli khuli nishanain unn logon ke samnay ayen to unhon ne kaha yeh to khula jaadoo hai
